---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>About Me | A Jammin Life</title>

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>


  <body>
    <Header />

    <main class="about-page">
      <h1>About Me: A Jammin Life</h1>

      <img
        src="/images/about_me.jpeg"
        alt="Jae from A Jammin Life"
        class="about-photo"
      />

      <section class="about-text">
        <p>
          I am Jammin: part-time chef, full-time dog mom, dexterous handicraftsman,
          matcha enthusiast, fainthearted adventurer, versatile innovator
          and most of all, a big dreamer!
        </p>

        <p>
          I’ve wanted to be a chef since I was 13 years old, but it took years of
          convincing for my parents to allow me to go to culinary school on one condition:
          that I pay for it myself. So I worked 3 part time jobs (overnight baker,
          dinnertime restaurant server, and weekend office clerk) while attending school.
        </p>

        <p>
          Despite running on fumes to afford school, I remember this time to be 
          the happiest I had been. The magical moment began every night at 2 AM
          when the world was asleep and the cafe would be the only flickering lights in the dark.
          Playing the Gorillaz’s “On Melancholy Hill” in the background, I baked croissants
          and pretzels, filling the air with the warm smell of sugar and butter. I watched
          the sun rise through the floor-to-ceiling windows as the baristas arrived to open.
          I traded fresh bread for my daily dose of caffeine, with the coffee smell blending
          into the kitchen. By then my shift would be over and I would head to class to join
          my newfound food-loving friends. Altogether, I was engulfed by the overwhelming sensations
          of good food, good people, and good atmosphere. Since then, I have been pursuing to
          feel that level of peaceful contentment again, and be able to share it with
          those around me through food.
        </p>
      </section>

    </main>

    <Footer />

    <script>
      const button = document.getElementById("menuButton");
      const menu = document.getElementById("menu");

      button?.addEventListener("click", () => {
        menu?.classList.toggle("open");
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Josefin Sans", sans-serif;
    color: #111;
    background: white;
  }

  header {
    height: 96px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #111;
  }

  .brand img {
    width: 58px;
    height: 58px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .brand span {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .menu-button {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-size: 2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: #111;
  }

  nav {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 80px;
    right: 4rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    z-index: 10;
  }

  nav.open {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  nav a {
    color: #111;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .about-page {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: min(560px, 85vw);
    height: min(560px, 85vw);
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .about-text {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.0vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 350;
  }


  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    header {
      height: 80px;
      padding: 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .brand img {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
    }

    .brand span {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    nav {
      right: 1.25rem;
      top: 70px;
    }

    .about-page {
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>